SUMMARY:Open Coffee Club
DESCRIPTION:Tech Lancaster Meetups\nEvery first Friday we visit Mean Cup a
 nd chat about whatever topics come to mind! Attendees tend to skew towards
  technology professionals and hobbyists so expect topics to follow that ge
 neral pattern.\n\n1 hour only! Check #open-coffee-club on [Slack](https://
 forms.gle/ih5iiLqk8YocutMF7) for the most up to date information.
